{"tid":657456,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[阿飛正傳] 究竟4月16號3點鐘有咩潛在意思","createTime":"2018-05-08T06:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T04:34:59.000Z","uid":49941,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9399573b1c24dd128c760c105058abaf78710b87","tid":657456,"uid":49941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:28:03.000Z","msg":"依套我睇左幾次, 身邊人都伙因為卡士好/橫掃金像獎而睇<br />\n<br />\n但我硬係覺得王家衛係有D野想表達,而佢亦有將D意思交比當年評審而令佢攞最佳電影<br />\n<br />\n其中對白:<br />\n<br />\n張國榮：今天幾號了？<br />\n<br />\n張曼玉：十六號。<br />\n<br />\n張國榮：十六號，四月十六號。一九六零年四月十六號下午三點之前的一分鐘你和我在一起，因為你我會記住這一分鐘。從現在開始我們就是一分鐘的朋友，這是事實，你改變不了，因為已經過去了。我明天會再來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://4bluestones.biz/mtblog/daysofbeingwild1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4bluestones.biz%2Fmtblog%2Fdaysofbeingwild1.jpg&h=c9ab03f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我自己就諗到4月16可能係講緊1987年4月16日鄧小平發表一國兩制香港回歸中國後<br />\n50年不變,而到另一幕劉華同哥哥對話<br />\n<br />\n劉德華：你可記得去年四月十六日下午三時你在幹什麼？<br />\n<br />\n張國榮：為什麼這樣問？<br />\n<br />\n劉德華：沒什麼。我有個朋友考我記憶力，她問我那天做了什麼，我可忘了，你呢？<br />\n<br />\n張國榮：是她告訴你的？<br />\n<br />\n劉德華：我還以為你忘記了。<br />\n<br />\n張國榮：要記住的我永遠都會記着的。你們有來往嗎？<br />\n<br />\n劉德華：一段時間。我跑船之後就沒聯絡了。你呢？<br />\n<br />\n張國榮：我？沒有了。她還跟你說了些什麼？<br />\n<br />\n劉德華：沒有了。我們只認識了一段很短的時間。<br />\n<br />\n張國榮：你很喜歡她嗎？<br />\n<br />\n劉德華：不是。只是朋友而已。<br />\n<br />\n張國榮：要是你有機會碰上她的話，你跟她說我什麼都忘了，這樣大家都會好過一點。<br />\n<br />\n表示緊王家衛想表達50年不變根本係9up <br />\n<br />\n但我又諗唔明點解要3點而唔係其他鐘數<br />\n<br />\n所以想係到集思廣益下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b89fd266e336128623d50828f07d0fe9a82581a","tid":657456,"uid":49941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe7826ea82562723c6770854905f70c1063ca41","tid":657456,"uid":49941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a598bd0460b1b21995aa6c2602468734e2ba8517","tid":657456,"uid":49941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fa337c3a575dcd8956b23988c13a23bc94f225","tid":657456,"uid":40350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"無意思"},{"pid":"4b6a5a3613df05e1471ea3032792eec6d0cd50ef","tid":657456,"uid":44461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"30fa337c3a575dcd8956b23988c13a23bc94f225","tid":657456,"uid":40350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"無意思"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:57:44.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n雖則我好鐘意王家衛啲戲<br />\n但佢啲戲有好多野你真係要解嘅話都可以係穿鑿附會"},{"pid":"71b52dfd45bb2abdd59bcf6aef8161ed23b2a936","tid":657456,"uid":49941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b6a5a3613df05e1471ea3032792eec6d0cd50ef","tid":657456,"uid":44461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"30fa337c3a575dcd8956b23988c13a23bc94f225","tid":657456,"uid":40350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"無意思"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T06:57:44.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n雖則我好鐘意王家衛啲戲<br />\n但佢啲戲有好多野你真係要解嘅話都可以係穿鑿附會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"純粹睇吓有無d唔同見解姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eca1c4a67b92d66e92a8d9ed3d556717fb065d4","tid":657456,"uid":1249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:02:51.000Z","msg":"唔好過份解讀"},{"pid":"79f06f179471741cf279a28ceb46ab9cac3f090a","tid":657456,"uid":153609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"